Running the Application:

Producer Command Example:
java -cp target/your-jar-file.jar com.kafka.KafkaManager -config dev01.properties -command producer -produceFilePath /path/to/messages.txt

Consumer Command Example:
java -cp target/your-jar-file.jar com.kafka.KafkaManager -config dev01.properties -command consumer -isSaveFile true -saveFilePath /path/to/save/messages.zip

Copy Command Example:
java -cp target/your-jar-file.jar com.kafka.KafkaManager -config dev01.properties -command copy -sourceTopic source-topic-name -destinationTopic destination-topic-name
